00:09:49.936 --> 00:09:53.710
do that, but these money rates
don't move totally on their own.

00:09:53.710 --> 00:09:55.874
They have to do,
and we said that Irving

00:09:55.874 --> 00:09:57.513
Fisher--
we haven't described Irving

00:09:57.513 --> 00:09:59.678
Fisher's theory of money and
nominal interest rates--

00:09:59.678 --> 00:10:02.118
