00:10:11.100 --> 00:10:15.519
So the Fed, in the crisis of
2008, you know,

00:10:15.519 --> 00:10:18.462
was terrified,
and it dropped the interest

00:10:18.462 --> 00:10:20.590
rate almost to 0,
virtually 0,

00:10:20.590 --> 00:10:24.014
and it's kept it there,
because from December 2008 till

00:10:24.014 --> 00:10:26.620
